Here we will have two cases
for positve and negative number as input

1) if the number is negative : we have to check whether the digit at current position is greater than ```x```
	if yes : then replace
	else continue

	finally, since nothing matched our if condition, we will simply place the number in the end.

2)  if the number is postive : we have to check whether the digit at current position is smaller than ```x```
	if yes : then replace
	else continue

	finally, since nothing matched our if condition, we will simply place the number in the end.

