# Approach
For Positive Numbers we insert x at the position that will Maximize the Number. The Position is where the value of string at that position is less than x. If there is no such Position, we add x to the end of the string. For Negative Numbers, we just do the opposite. We insert x at the position where the value of string at that position is greater than x. If there is no such Position, we add x at the end of the string.
<!-- Describe your approach to solving the problem. -->

